; Coverage for filters.cc changed_value_posts output_revaluation
; and output_intermediate_prices paths
; Tests market gain/loss revaluation with price history

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/01/15 AAPL $160.00
P 2024/02/01 AAPL $155.00

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --market --gain
24-Jan-15 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                  $100.00      $100.00
24-Feb-01 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                  $-50.00       $50.00
end test
